{"tid":1746849,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"NOW: 湯建議人大「澄清」確認緊急法符合基本法  一請問「澄清」和「釋法」有什麼分別？","createTime":"2019-11-23T02:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T04:04:21.000Z","uid":252356,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ca76cc0eb3301324d3db316f8f1179e0b53dd722","tid":1746849,"uid":252356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:55:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">請問各位大大「澄清」和「釋法」有什麼分別？<br />\n面皮太厚了吧</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=370918&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D370918%26refer%3DShare&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvghx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=c0ebd6d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D370918%26refer%3DShare&h=a7865484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=370918&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">湯建議人大「澄清」確認緊急法符合基本法</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】高等法院裁定禁蒙面法違憲，行政會議成員湯家驊接受《大鳴大放》訪問時稱，中央可透過「澄清」的方式，確認回歸前人大常委會已將緊急法納入香港的法律，符合基本法，相信此做法比人大釋法好。<br />\n<br />\n高等法院裁定政府引用緊急法制訂禁蒙面法不符合基本法後，法工委、港澳辦都批評裁決。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員湯家驊接受《大鳴大放》專訪時，亦對法院的裁決感到驚訝，建議人大常委會在釋法以外，透過其他方式確認緊急法符合基本法。至於四中全會提出，要完善特首及主要官員的任免機制，他認是中央是想為將來普選做準備。<br />\n<br />\n至於何時就23條立法，湯家驊認為，若有人提出現在就要立法，是完全漠視政治形勢。"},{"pid":"d9d5f617030b9a4d526491cfc2dfe232d50d07e1","tid":1746849,"uid":51436,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:01:18.000Z","msg":"咁衰11需唔需要澄清？"},{"pid":"b41797f91ad7174fd4287402cf9575ff090844f1","tid":1746849,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/npc-12272017083905.html/npc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcanton